ghost-role-information-monolithic-generic-name = Monolithic Entity
ghost-role-information-monolithic-generic-description = A mysterious mass of energy, emerged from the infinite aether, the void, Heaven, Hell, somewhere.
ghost-role-information-monolithic-generic-rules = Your only allies are [color=#cd42ff][bold]other monolithic entities[/bold][/color].
                                                  Your goal is to [color=#cd42ff][bold]defend the mythic energies of your spawnpoint[/bold][/color].
                                                  You [bold]should [color=#cd42ff]not leave your origin[/color] for ANY reason.[/bold] Should you be forcefully removed, you must attempt to return.
                                                  You must [color=red][bold]not[/bold] round-remove or gib[/color] intruders. Leave them as dead.
                                                  You don't remember any of your previous life, and you don't remember anything you learned as a ghost.
                                                  You are allowed to remember knowledge about the game in general, such as how to cook, how to use objects, etc.
                                                  You are absolutely [color=red]NOT[/color] allowed to remember the name, appearance, etc. of your previous character.
